## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="00e29-102">A <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> 개체는 여러 가지 값 중 하나를 가질 수 있는 구문의 구성 요소를 나타냅니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-102">A <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> object represents a component of a phrase that can have one of several values.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="00e29-103">음성 인식에서 문법을 만들 때이 클래스를 사용 하 여 한 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-103">Use this class when creating a speech recognition grammar from a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> object.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="00e29-104">예를 들어 한 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> 개체 구성 요소를 나타낼 수 *colorChoice* 는 구에서의 "색을 변경 하 *colorChoice*" 여기서 사용할 수 있는 값에 대 한 *colorChoice* "red" 또는 "녹색" 또는 "blue"입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-104">For example, a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> object could represent the component *colorChoice* in the phrase, "Change the color to *colorChoice*", where acceptable values for *colorChoice* are "red", or "green", or "blue".</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="00e29-105">사용 하는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> 는 구에서의 선택적 구성 요소로 개체를 만들기는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> 개체에 추가 하는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.%23ctor%28System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29?displayProperty=nameWithType> 개체 `minRepeat` 및 `maxRepeat` 각각 0과 1로 설정 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-105">To use a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> object as an optional component in a phrase, create the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> object and add it to a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.%23ctor%28System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29?displayProperty=nameWithType> object with `minRepeat` and `maxRepeat` set to 0 and 1, respectively.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="00e29-106">구 선택적 구성 요소를 포함 하는 선택적 구성 요소에서 사용 되는 여부 인식할 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-106">Phrases containing optional components can be recognized whether or not the optional component is spoken.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="00e29-107"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> 이 클래스와 동일한 기능을 사용는 `one-of` 에 정의 된 XML 요소는 [음성 인식 문법 사양 (SRGS) 버전 1.0](https://www.w3.org/TR/speech-grammar/) 와 비슷합니다는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> 클래스에 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar> 네임 스페이스입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-107">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> class serves the same function as the `one-of` XML element defined by the [Speech Recognition Grammar Specification (SRGS) Version 1.0](https://www.w3.org/TR/speech-grammar/) and is similar to the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> class in the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar> namespace.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="00e29-108">음성 인식 문법을 정의 하는 방법에 대 한 자세한 내용은 참조 [음성 인식](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/6a7dc524-07fc-4862-8d48-8c10dc64b919) 및 [GrammarBuilder 문법 만드는](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/7e2cc577-cb05-4318-9da3-7c8675d3d9ae)합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-108">For more information about defining a speech recognition grammar, see [Speech Recognition](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/6a7dc524-07fc-4862-8d48-8c10dc64b919) and [Creating GrammarBuilder Grammars](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/7e2cc577-cb05-4318-9da3-7c8675d3d9ae).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="00e29-109">다음 예에서는 구문을 음성 인식 문법 "배경 설정 *colorChoice*" 여기서 *colorChoice* 정의 된 색 중 하나일 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-109">The following example creates a speech recognition grammar for the phrase, "Set background to *colorChoice*", where *colorChoice* can be one of the defined colors.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="00e29-110"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> 문법에 대 한 제약 조건을 정의 하는 데 사용 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-110">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> is used to define the constraints for the grammar.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
  
private Grammar CreateColorGrammar()  
{  
  
  // Create a Choices object that contains a set of alternative colors.  
  Choices colorChoice = new Choices(new string[] {"red", "green", "blue"});  
  colorChoice.Add(new string[] {"cyan", "yellow", "magenta"});  
  
  // Construct the phrase.  
  GrammarBuilder builder = new GrammarBuilder("Set background to");  
  builder.Append(colorChoice);  
  
  // Create a grammar for the phrase.  
  Grammar colorGrammar = new Grammar(builder);  
  colorGrammar.Name = "SetBackground";  
  
  return colorGrammar;  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="00e29-112">생성할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> 개체 되는 기본 생성자 (빈 개체 반환), 그룹에서 사용 하 여 <xref:System.String> 개체 또는 집합에서 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-112">You can construct a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> object using a default constructor (which returns an empty object), from a group of <xref:System.String> objects, or a from set of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> objects.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="00e29-113">때문에 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> 개체가 암시적으로 변환 지원 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> 및 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultKey>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> 캐스트를 사용 하 여 이러한 개체의 배열에서 생성 될 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-113">Because the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> object supports implicit conversion from <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultKey>, a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> can be constructed from an array of these objects using a cast.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="00e29-114">다음 예제에서는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> 개체를 대체 하는 두 개의 목록을 만듭니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-114">The following example uses <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> objects to create two lists of alternatives.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="00e29-115">첫 번째 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> 개체의 배열에서 생성 되 <xref:System.String> 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-115">The first <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> object is constructed from an array of <xref:System.String> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="00e29-116">다른 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> 개체의 배열에서 생성 되 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> 한 캐스트 암시적으로 변환 하는 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-116">The other <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> object is constructed from an array of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> objects which have been implicitly converted by a cast.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="00e29-117">이 예제에서는 사용는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> 을 문구를 조합 하는 개체를 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> 개체 및 음성 인식 하는 데 사용할 수 있는 두 개의 추가 문자열 입력 "호출 [contactlList] [phoneType] 전화에" 형식의 예를 들어 "휴대 전화에 전화 Jane"입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-117">The example uses a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> object to assemble a phrase, using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> objects and two additional strings, that can be used to recognize speech input in the form of "Call [contactlList] on [phoneType] phone" , for example "Call Jane on cell phone".</span></span>  
  
```  
public GrammarBuilder ChoicesContructor2 ()  
{  
    GrammarBuilder gb = new GrammarBuilder ();  
    Choices phoneType = new Choices (new string[] {"cell", "home", "work"});  
    Choices contactList = new Choices (new GrammarBuilder[] {(GrammarBuilder) "Mark", (GrammarBuilder) "Jane", (GrammarBuilder) "Frank"});  
    gb.Append ("Call");  
    gb.Append (contactList);  
    gb.Append ("on");  
    gb.Append (phoneType);  
    gb.Append ("phone");  
    return gb;  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="00e29-119">이 생성자는 대안의 유효한, 빈 집합을 반환합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-119">This constructor returns a valid, empty set of alternatives.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="00e29-120">중 하나를 사용 하 여 대안을 추가할 수는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices.Add%2A> 메서드.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-120">You can add alternatives using any of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices.Add%2A> methods.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="00e29-121">다음 예제에서는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> 및 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> 개체는 "호출 Anne 그녀의 셀에" 및 "자신의 회사 전화에 전화 James" 등의 음성 입력을 인식 하는 데 사용할 수는 문구를 만들려고 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-121">The following example uses <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> objects to create a phrase that can be used to recognize speech input such as "Call Anne on her cell" and "Call James on his work phone".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="00e29-122">이 예제에서 암시적 캐스트를 사용 하 여 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> 및 <xref:System.String> 를 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-122">The example uses implicit casts from <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> and <xref:System.String> to <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
public Grammar CreatePhonePhrase()  
{  
  
  // Create alternatives for female names and add a phrase.  
  GrammarBuilder females = new Choices(new string[] { "Anne", "Mary" });  
  females.Append("on her");  
  
  // Create alternatives for male names and add a phrase.  
  GrammarBuilder males = new Choices(new string[] { "James", "Sam" });  
  males.Append("on his");  
  
  // Create a Choices object that contains an array of alternative  
  // GrammarBuilder objects.  
  Choices people = new Choices();  
  people.Add(new Choices(new GrammarBuilder[] {females, males}));  
  
  // Create a Choices object that contains a set of alternative phone types.  
  Choices phoneType = new Choices();  
  phoneType.Add(new string[] { "cell", "home", "work" });  
  
  // Construct the phrase.  
  GrammarBuilder gb = new GrammarBuilder();  
  gb.Append("call");  
  gb.Append(people);  
  gb.Append(phoneType);  
  gb.Append(new GrammarBuilder("phone"), 0, 1);  
  
  return new Grammar(gb);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="00e29-125">각 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> 에 `alternateChoices` 하나를 정의 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-125">Each <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> in `alternateChoices` defines one alternative.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="00e29-126">경우 `alternateChoices` (가) 빈 배열 생성자 대안의 빈 집합을 반환 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-126">If `alternateChoices` is an empty array, the constructor returns an empty set of alternatives.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="00e29-127">중 하나를 사용 하 여 대안을 추가할 수는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices.Add%2A> 메서드.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-127">You can add alternatives using any of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices.Add%2A> methods.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="00e29-128">생성자를 throw 한 <xref:System.ArgumentNullException> 때 `alternateChoices` 은 `null` 는 배열 요소가 또는 `null`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-128">The constructor throws an <xref:System.ArgumentNullException> when `alternateChoices` is `null` or when any of the array elements are `null`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="00e29-129">때문에 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> 클래스가 암시적으로 변환에 대 한 지원을 제공 하므로 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue>, 및 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultKey> 개체를 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> 인스턴스 캐스트를 올바르게 사용 하 여이 생성자 사용할 수도 있습니다를 만드는 한 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> 이러한 개체의 조합 목록에서 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-129">Because the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> class provides support for implicit conversion of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue>, and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultKey> objects to <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> instances, by properly using casts, this constructor can also be used to create a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> object from a list of any combination of these objects.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="00e29-130">다음 예제에서는 `Choices` 및 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> 개체를 만드는 한 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> 예: "호출 Anne 그녀의 셀에" 및 "자신의 회사 전화에 전화 James"는 구입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-130">The following example uses `Choices` and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> objects to create a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> for phrases such as, "Call Anne on her cell" and "Call James on his work phone".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="00e29-131">이 예제에서 암시적 캐스트를 사용 하 여 `Choices` 및 <xref:System.String> 를 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e29-131">The example uses implicit casts from `Choices` and <xref:System.String> to <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder>.</span></span>  
  
